{"word":"Sowing and Reaping","slug":"sowing-and-reaping","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sowing and Reaping</b> - <b>(A) SOWING EVIL,</b> on the part of the wicked<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=4&verse=8'>Job 4:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=6&verse=14'>Pro 6:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=16&verse=28'>Pro 16:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=22&verse=8'>Pro 22:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=8&verse=7'>Hos 8:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=6&verse=8'>Gal 6:8</a><p/><b>(B) HARVEST OF SIN</b><p/><b>Disappointing</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=17&verse=11'>Isa 17:11</a><p/><b>Profitless</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=12&verse=13'>Jer 12:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=33'>Jer 51:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=6&verse=11'>Hos 6:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=8&verse=7'>Hos 8:7</a><p/><b>Reaped at the Judgment Day</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=12'>Joe 3:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=13'>Joe 3:13</a><p/><b>According to the Seed Sown</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=6&verse=7'>Gal 6:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=6&verse=8'>Gal 6:8</a><p/><b>Sure to Come in the Fulness of Time</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=14&verse=15'>Re 14:15</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Sin's Misery, MISERY<p/>Wages of Sin, LOSS<p/><b>(C) SOWING, SPIRITUAL,</b> the blessings of<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=126&verse=5'>Psa 126:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=12